  "name": "Manage Your JetSend Profile",
  "body": "<p>Click your user name on the top-right corner of the application and from the drop-down menu, select Account Settings. The Account Settings page opens and displays the PROFILE tab.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"blockquote\">You can reset your login password in the PROFILE tab; however, if you want to change your login email address, you must contact us at <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:support@jetsend.com\">support@jetsend.com</a>.</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"346\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png\" width=\"700\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 346px; width: 700px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/1.05T5g00000Ao5NBEAZ.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>",
